  "title": "Warehouse Officer (Multiple Openings, Various Location)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Perform general warehouse duties and ensure smooth daily logistic operations</p></li><li><p>Receive and inspect inbound shipments and complete required log sheets</p></li><li><p>Verify supplier returns and accurately record order receipts</p></li><li><p>Relocate, consolidate, and organize materials within the warehouse</p></li><li><p>Prepare and assemble packing lists for outbound orders</p></li><li><p>Pack, label, wrap, and load goods for shipment</p></li><li><p>Maintain cleanliness and organization of assigned work areas</p></li><li><p>Follow safety procedures and operational guidelines</p></li><li><p>Ad hoc duties as required.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Nitec in Business Administration, Logistics & Supply Chain or equivalent</p></li><li><p>With 1 - 2 years of warehouse & logistics operations experience, preferably from FMCG/ Food Manufacturing industry</p></li></ul><p><br />Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please send in your updated resume to <a href=\"mailto:gs1@talenttradersg.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>gs1@talenttradersg.com</strong></a> </p><p><br />EA License No: 13C6305<br />Reg. No.: R24120209 (<strong>GAN CHYE SHEN</strong>)</p><p>For candidate who applied for the advertised position is deemed to have consented to us that we may collect, use or disclose your personal information for purpose in connection with the services provided by us.</p>",
